19-07-19T16:54:36.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55602b7380fc9f729119efa2816c102caac0bbf1","tid":1333436,"uid":101151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82814c0a9fea1786c073b42285b88a78e65b33a0","tid":1333436,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:53:15.000Z","msg":"估計黑警恨不得快d到21號上裝打撚死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:07:29.000Z","msg":"今日咁嘅地步，乜方法都要試。老實講，唔係唔想贏，但係真係唔想見到再有人命傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n如果佢哋係聽我講，我哋就可以用最低成本、最安全嘅方法解決今次嘅紛爭。<br />\n<br />\n應該仆街嗰個係港共政權，唔應該係我哋班星斗市民"},{"pid":"3c18241b97e75ed59c68d2451530aefbd6d92a1e","tid":1333436,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:08:18.000Z","msg":"雖然你講得好理想，但現實係相反，負評左，sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fed6d3da9a3193a1a930399e37d3dff9bf4083a","tid":1333436,"uid":101151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:10:06.000Z","msg":"起碼推到佢哋睇到呀，信唔信我係一回事。<br />\n方法俾咗你，阿sir、madam 你哋可以繼續打呢場毫無意義嘅戰爭，亦都可以用第二個方法，將一切混亂平息。<br />\n<br />\n所有嘢仲係有得救，支持罷工，聲討盧偉聰！"},{"pid":"35705a020c502b86506c7ba3ef1e59efcbdc8bbd","tid":1333436,"uid":101151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c18241b97e75ed59c68d2451530aefbd6d92a1e","tid":1333436,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:08:18.000Z","msg":"雖然你講得好理想，但現實係相反，負評左，sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:12:03.000Z","msg":"都無所謂，推到佢哋睇到為止就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60007e92d699d7d5fd13f425f198b9b0da42f524","tid":1333436,"uid":120101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T19:11:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"